 150    private static bool SetGifBlock(byte[] gifBytes, ref int byteIndex, ref GifData gifData)
 151    {
 152        try
 153        {
 6154            int lastIndex = 0;
 546155            while (true)
 156            {
 552157                int nowIndex = byteIndex;
 158
 552159                if (gifBytes[nowIndex] == 0x2c)
 160                {
 161                    // Image Block(0x2c)
 270162                    SetImageBlock(gifBytes, ref byteIndex, ref gifData);
 163
 270164                }
 282165                else if (gifBytes[nowIndex] == 0x21)
 166                {
 167                    // Extension
 276168                    switch (gifBytes[nowIndex + 1])
 169                    {
 170                        case 0xf9:
 171                            // Graphic Control Extension(0x21 0xf9)
 270172                            SetGraphicControlExtension(gifBytes, ref byteIndex, ref gifData);
 270173                            break;
 174                        case 0xfe:
 175                            // Comment Extension(0x21 0xfe)
 0176                            SetCommentExtension(gifBytes, ref byteIndex, ref gifData);
 0177                            break;
 178                        case 0x01:
 179                            // Plain Text Extension(0x21 0x01)
 0180                            SetPlainTextExtension(gifBytes, ref byteIndex, ref gifData);
 0181                            break;
 182                        case 0xff:
 183                            // Application Extension(0x21 0xff)
 6184                            SetApplicationExtension(gifBytes, ref byteIndex, ref gifData);
 6185                            break;
 186                        default:
 187                            break;
 188                    }
 189                }
 6190                else if (gifBytes[nowIndex] == 0x3b)
 191                {
 192                    // Trailer(1 Byte)
 6193                    gifData.m_trailer = gifBytes[byteIndex];
 6194                    byteIndex++;
 6195                    break;
 196                }
 197
 546198                if (lastIndex == nowIndex)
 199                {
 0200                    Debug.LogError("Infinite loop error.");
 0201                    return false;
 202                }
 203
 546204                lastIndex = nowIndex;
 205            }
 6206        }
 207        catch (Exception ex)
 208        {
 0209            Debug.LogError(ex.Message);
 0210            return false;
 211        }
 212
 6213        return true;
 0214    }
